    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《睡眠时》是一款第一人称恐怖游戏，讲述了体验睡眠麻痹的过程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你正在睡觉，明天要去上班，结果你得了睡眠麻痹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的身体瘫痪了，你动弹不得，除了环顾四周或闭上眼睛再睁开，你什么也做不了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你瘫痪的睡眠中，你必须通过体验周围出现的鬼魂和令人毛骨悚然的现象来生存到天亮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时间：平均 15 ~ 30 分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意：与真正的睡眠麻痹不同，某些内容可能会被夸大以营造恐怖氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>睡眠麻痹</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/be55286bf16d9796feb6af16f87aceb7.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你无法移动你的身体。你只能睁开或闭上眼睛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>令人毛骨悚然的现象</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/d3cee1bf2d4e1a4b71f8c5eb37ba98ea.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>随着时间的推移，令人毛骨悚然的现象不断出现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>不要被鬼魂抓住</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/cf2da45de95fe0b00e640f31163f2fed.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>出现的每个鬼魂都有不同的行动方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>生存到太阳升起</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.poster.avif?t=1734016345\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.webm?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396190/extras/85ca37c31f0ca34becb0e53eb87ffef1.mp4?t=1734016345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你必须生存到摆脱睡眠麻痹。</p>",
